{"tid":1226989,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"人地跳樓你班狗拎住個盾係咩事呀","createTime":"2019-06-15T14:08:44.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-15T14:54:46.000Z","uid":68215,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"3d3e819c72913d8b3578a3671a267c3532075ff2","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:08:44.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">係唔係啲白衫用個屎忽諗嘢你地就盲從呀<br />\n人地白衫當你安全套咋<br />\n值得咩？</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Ozouuch.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FOzouuch.png&h=1c96a018&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"28665e9021abc03663336a5f2309b96f62604d5e","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:09:28.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e634c46c50f4813ba12dbee8b55dcdfd66fc8b63","tid":1226989,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c4bb7728de51020fa438836634a0e421aa591265","tid":1226989,"uid":259518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:13:45.000Z","msg":"驚佢身上有炸彈會炸死自己掛<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/frownsmile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"be919df65bea2bd3fb4c3d30f611037121c05922","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"e634c46c50f4813ba12dbee8b55dcdfd66fc8b63","tid":1226989,"uid":157362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:10:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:14:22.000Z","msg":"唔猜測佢用意<br />\n不過佢呢啲時刻都拎住個盾就有問題<br />\n好似隨時都要鎮壓噉<br />\n你班狗到底有幾反社會先做得出"},{"pid":"e0a6a5a393963d634b69039ca9267137ad5cdcff","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0ec471bc24659b7ef9603177e65a7882fada7d1","tid":1226989,"uid":123050,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:22:02.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>行政機關濫用權力之審判</strong></span><br />\n二戰末期，納粹德國敗局已現，佛斯曼醫師、門格勒、拉舍爾三人的命運也隨著戰爭快速流轉。1945年時，拉舍爾因犯罪而被處死，和被他殺死的許多人一樣，葬身於達豪集中營裡。而門格勒假扮成一般士兵，躲過追緝後流亡到南美洲，直到1979年在巴西意外溺斃後才被確認身分。而始終堅持人性的佛斯曼醫師則在戰火中存活了下來，1945年時游過易北河後向美軍投降，戰後以泌尿科醫師的身份默默地生活著。在惡魔的年代結束之際，三名醫師分別擁來了他們各自的結局&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://pansci.asia/wp-content/uploads/2015/12/5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpansci.asia%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2015%2F12%2F5bd929a85b8a970c9c8fd7567b295223-e1450778342448.jpg&h=327c7f1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n左上圖：將人浸入冰水當中，藉此研究在低溫下人體的反應；左下圖：故意讓小孩感染結核菌，並切除腋下的淋巴腺，測試人體的免疫力；右圖：紐倫堡審判中，對卡爾&middot;勃蘭特（Karl Brandt）醫師的審判，他被控同意並參與非人道實驗和其他戰爭罪行，最後被判絞刑。<br />\n用屍體換來的規範－紐倫堡守則<br />\n堆積如山的屍體、骨瘦如柴的幸存者，那些泯滅人性的實驗震撼了全世界。1948年在紐倫堡進行的醫師審判，被告的醫師之中，不乏知名的科學家，如施靈（Klaus Karl Schilling）曾是國際瘧疾研究聯盟的成員，戰時卻刻意讓一千多名囚犯感染瘧疾來進行科學研究。科學家在戰爭期間荒唐的行徑，讓美國醫師里昂&middot;亞歷山大（Leo Alexander）動筆起草人體實驗中應有的道德規範，也就是今日我們熟知的「紐倫堡公約」，寫明了醫師在任何情況之下，都不得傷害受試者（除非受試者就是醫師本人）。而1964年在芬蘭舉辦的全球醫師大會更提出「赫爾辛基宣言（The Declaration of Helsinki）」，說明了受試者有絕對的權利了解實驗內容，保障了受試者「知情同意」的權益。數十年的努力之下，美國和其他國家都誓言杜絕非人道的臨床實驗，全世界都認為這種惡魔般的人體實驗不會再出現了&hellip;&hellip;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qp60jU2.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqp60jU2.png&h=0f218e09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://scontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net/v/t1.0-9/62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg?_nc_cat=1&amp;_nc_ht=scontent.fhkg4-2.fna&amp;oh=af8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909&amp;oe=5D8A89DA\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fscontent.fhkg4-2.fna.fbcdn.net%2Fv%2Ft1.0-9%2F62254048_1233250940184671_5825174709460795392_n.jpg%3F_nc_cat%3D1%26_nc_ht%3Dscontent.fhkg4-2.fna%26oh%3Daf8a127ef43e169c16b9bc1668a17909%26oe%3D5D8A89DA&h=582c6bc5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"c044a0b4d7c8d4480367006af7987da5657ba506","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:26:54.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">特區政府 警隊<br />\n你地又背負多一條人命</span></span>"},{"pid":"3128253937770da401be3b597c0ab234476ddd10","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:37:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b9917e100fbdb4018d8f7487eedb4d87dd7fd159","tid":1226989,"uid":68215,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:47:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sBFwHJZ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsBFwHJZ.jpg&h=14117205&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n烈士背影<br />\n殺人政權 定有報應"},{"pid":"c0a9d23304b55e78a3ba4d33473a2825676fd940","tid":1226989,"uid":159920,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T14:54:46.000Z","msg":"推 好心痛"}]}